{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"12293-bed-time-stories","title":"Bed-Time Stories","description":"Let's all curl up in our blankets! This is a story about the stories that a mother tells her son before he sleeps.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"portrait","authors":["Kanchan Bannerjee"],"illustrators":["Harshvardhan Gantha"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/12293-bed-time-stories"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34952/size3/cd9982004d7e6ea392ebe738a42cb276.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34952/size6/cd9982004d7e6ea392ebe738a42cb276.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34800/size6/42dd71600197b2e6689fbad302e7d877.jpg","text":"My Amma tells me \na story every night.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34804/size6/9913769fd7fd8c4433e624145e62aef4.jpg","text":"There is one story about \na frog which talks.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34805/size6/99d1e384637c3509c8cdb183720e3068.jpg","text":"There is another story about \na king with a long beard.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34806/size6/786b3b0053a8c5f2ecd30132f12c9aa7.jpg","text":"Sometimes it is about \na flying elephant.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34807/size6/cf10c3d48f9d2ad1415e78c3633e46a9.jpg","text":"In one story a fox and a tiger are friends.\nThe tiger falls into a hole.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34808/size6/054c2f02c4dec1600dfaca4edeeb4bca.jpg","text":"How will the tiger get out?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/34809/size6/5095431c4a5ef017f692fc0ce5c3373c.jpg","text":"Then the clever fox saves the tiger. This is the\nbest story.\nI listen to the story and then fall asleep.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":78}}